   * makefile.bc
   * makefile.dc
   * makefile.gc
   * makefile.pc
   * makefile.vc
   * makefile.wc
     - dettaching ZLIB components from xHarbour RTL
     /*
      Note:
      These changes were tested under Windows Platform and it should work for:
      BCC 5.82, MSVC 6, XCC 2.70, PellesC 5.0b3, MinGW 3.4.5-2, OpenWatcom 1.7a
      and DigitalMars 8.51.

      ZLIB sources were taken AS-IS with minor changes on function interface
      to enable compilation with all of the above mentioned compilers.

      Developers of other platform are kindly requested to incorporate necessary
      modification if so required, as I was not able do it.

      No force-linking has been introduced yet until a situation proves that it
      is really required.

      GNU makefiles should be modified.
     */

