2008-03-18 22:35 UTC+0300 Phil Krylov <phil a t newstar.rinet.ru>
  * utils/hbrun/hbrun.prg
    * Change STATIC PROCEDURE Main() into FUNCTION _APPMAIN() to avoid:
      1) problems with locating start procedure on some platforms
      2) collision with user function in HRB file with that name.
      3) loss of return value.
    + Added a NOTE about this by Chen Kedem.

